role_description: An Ansible role that installs Parallels on macOS
role_description_full_overview: [Parallels Desktop for Mac](https://www.parallels.com/) is software providing hardware virtualization for Macintosh computers with Intel processors. It is developed by Parallels, since 2018 a subsidiary of Corel.
role_description_alt: This repository is the home of an Ansible role that installs Parallels on macOS.
